#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using JDK Flight Recorder"
msgstr "使用 JDK 飞行记录器"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide explains how https://openjdk.org/jeps/328[Flight Recorder] can be extended to provide additional insight into your Quarkus application.\n"
"JFR records various information from the Java standard API and JVM as events.\n"
"By adding the Quarkus JFR extension, you can add custom Quarkus events to JFR. This will help you solve potential problems in your application."
msgstr "本指南介绍了如何扩展 link:https://openjdk.org/jeps/328[Flight Recorder，] 以便更深入地了解您的 Quarkus 应用程序。JFR 会将 Java 标准 API 和 JVM 中的各种信息作为事件进行记录。通过添加 Quarkus JFR 扩展，您可以向 JFR 中添加自定义的 Quarkus 事件。这将有助于您解决应用程序中的潜在问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This document is part of the xref:observability.adoc[Observability in Quarkus reference guide] which features this and other observability related components."
msgstr "本文档是《 xref:observability.adoc[Quarkus 可观测性参考指南] 》的一部分，该指南介绍了本组件以及其他与可观测性相关的组件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"JFR can be preconfigured to dump a file, and when the application exits, JFR will output the file.\n"
"The file will contain the content of the JFR event stream to which Quarkus custom events have also been added.\n"
"You can, of course, get this file at any time you want, even if your application exits unexpectedly."
msgstr "JFR 可以预先配置为生成一个文件，当应用程序退出时，JFR 会输出该文件。该文件将包含 JFR 事件流的内容，其中还包含已添加的 Quarkus 自定义事件。当然，您可以随时获取该文件，即使应用程序意外退出也不例外。"

