#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Native Image"
msgstr "原生图像"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Native executables supports JDK Flight Recorder.\n"
"This extension also supports native executables."
msgstr "本机可执行文件支持 JDK Flight Recorder。该扩展同样支持本机可执行文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To enable JFR on native executables, it is usually built with `--enable-monitoring`.\n"
"However, we can enable JFR in Quarkus native executables by adding `jfr` to the configuration property `quarkus.native.monitoring`.\n"
"There are two ways to set up this configuration: by including it in the `application.properties` or by specifying it at build time."
msgstr "要在本机可执行文件中启用 JFR，通常需要在构建时使用 `--enable-monitoring` 选项。不过，我们也可以通过在配置属性 `quarkus.native.monitoring` 中添加 `jfr` 来启用 Quarkus 本机可执行文件中的 JFR。 有两种方式可以设置此配置：将其包含在 `application.properties` 中，或者在构建时进行指定。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The first method is to first configure settings in `application.properties`."
msgstr "第一种方法是先在 `application.properties` 文件中配置相关设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then build your native executable as usual:"
msgstr "然后像往常一样构建您的本机可执行文件："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The second way is to pass `-Dquarkus.native.monitoring=jfr` at build time:"
msgstr "第二种方法是在构建时传入 `-Dquarkus.native.monitoring=jfr` 参数："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Once you have finished building the native executable, you can run the native application with JFR as follows:"
msgstr "完成本机可执行文件的构建后，您可以按照以下方式使用 JFR 运行本机应用程序："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note that at this time, Mandrel and GraalVM cannot record JFR for Windows native executables."
msgstr "请注意，目前 Mandrel 和 GraalVM 无法为 Windows 本机可执行文件记录 JFR。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "JFR configuration"
msgstr "JFR 配置"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We can use the JFR CLI to configure the events that JFR will record.\n"
"The configuration file, JFC file, is in XML format, so we can modify it with a text editor.\n"
"However, it is recommended to use `jfr configure`, which is included in OpenJDK by default."
msgstr "我们可以使用 JFR 命令行界面 (CLI) 来配置 JFR 将记录的事件。配置文件（JFC 文件）采用 XML 格式，因此我们可以使用文本编辑器对其进行修改。不过，建议使用 `jfr configure` 命令，该命令默认包含在 OpenJDK 中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here we create a configuration file in which REST Start and REST End events are recorded (they are not recorded by default):"
msgstr "在此，我们创建一个配置文件，用于记录 REST Start 和 REST End 事件（默认情况下这些事件不会被记录）："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This creates `custom-rest.jfc` as a configuration file with recording for RestStart and RestEnd enabled."
msgstr "这将生成一个名为 `custom-rest.jfc` 的配置文件，其中启用了 RestStart 和 RestEnd 的日志记录功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now we are ready to run our application with the new settings.\n"
"We launch the application with JFR configured so that it is enabled from the startup of the Java Virtual Machine."
msgstr "现在，我们已经准备好使用新的设置运行应用程序了。我们启动应用程序时，已配置好 JFR，使其在 Java 虚拟机启动时即被启用。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Adding new events"
msgstr "添加新活动"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This section is for extension authors who want to add new JFR events."
msgstr "本节面向希望添加新 JFR 事件的扩展作者。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Depending on the API module"
msgstr "取决于 API 模块"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Quarkus JFR extension separates the public API from the runtime implementation.\n"
"As a result, other extensions can implement JFR-based instrumentation by depending only on the JFR API module, without adding a dependency on the Quarkus JFR extension implementation itself."
msgstr "Quarkus JFR 扩展将公共 API 与运行时实现分离。因此，其他扩展只需依赖 JFR API 模块，即可实现基于 JFR 的插桩，而无需依赖 Quarkus JFR 扩展的实现本身。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "At deployment time, an extension can detect whether the application has enabled the Quarkus JFR extension by using Quarkus capabilities:"
msgstr "在部署时，扩展可以通过 Quarkus 功能检测应用程序是否已启用 Quarkus JFR 扩展："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This pattern allows your extension to:\n"
"* compile against stable API types only, and\n"
"* activate JFR instrumentation only when the Quarkus JFR extension is present in the application."
msgstr "此模式可让您的扩展：* 仅针对稳定的 API 类型进行编译，以及 * 仅在应用程序中存在 Quarkus JFR 扩展时才激活 JFR 插桩功能。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Associating events by request"
msgstr "根据请求关联事件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We recommend that new events be associated with existing events.\n"
"Associations are useful when looking at the details of a process that is taking a long time.\n"
"For example, a general REST application retrieves the data needed for processing from a datastore.\n"
"If REST events are not associated with datastore events, it is impossible to know which datastore events were processed in each REST request.\n"
"When the two events are associated, we know immediately which datastore event was processed in each REST request."
msgstr "我们建议将新事件与现有事件建立关联。在分析耗时较长的流程细节时，这种关联非常有用。 例如，一个典型的 REST 应用程序会从数据存储中检索处理所需的数据。如果 REST 事件未与数据存储事件建立关联，就无法得知每个 REST 请求中处理了哪些数据存储事件。当这两类事件建立关联后，我们就能立即知道每个 REST 请求中处理了哪个数据存储事件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Datastore events are not implemented yet."
msgstr "数据存储事件尚未实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Quarkus JFR extension provides a Request ID for event association.\n"
"See <<identifying-requests>> for more information on Request IDs."
msgstr "Quarkus JFR 扩展为事件关联提供了请求 ID。有关请求 ID 的更多信息，请参阅 <<identifying-requests>> 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In code, you typically need the following two steps."
msgstr "在代码中，通常需要执行以下两个步骤。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "1) Add trace/span identifiers to your event"
msgstr "1) 在您的事件中添加跟踪/跨度标识符"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Implement `traceId` and `spanId` on the new event as follows.\n"
"The `@TraceIdRelational` and `@SpanIdRelational` annotations mark these fields as relational identifiers used for association."
msgstr "请按以下方式在新事件上实现 `traceId` 和 `spanId` 。 `@TraceIdRelational` 和 `@SpanIdRelational` 注解将这些字段标记为用于关联的关系标识符。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "2) Populate the identifiers from the IdProducer"
msgstr "2) 从 IdProducer 中获取标识符"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/jfr.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Obtain the values to store in the event from an `IdProducer` and set them just before committing the event."
msgstr "从 `IdProducer` 中获取要存储在事件中的值，并在提交事件之前将其设置好。"

